    "Through this methodology, the PGN can effectively mitigate the issue of duplicate generation and enhance the quality of text summarization.",
    "The coverage vector c t tracks the words that have been gen- erated and applies a certain penalty to these words to minimize the duplication in the generated summary.",
    "c t can be understood as the degree of coverage that the words have received from the attention mechanism, then the coverage vector is regarded as extra input into the attention mechanism.",
